elements.name: I can login into the CMS application

steps.name: Login: I am on the "/"
Login: I close "newUXLoginPopup"
Login: I fill "k900378" in "Username"
Login: I fill "pswpsw123" in "Password"
Login: I wait for "1" seconds
Login: I click on "Login button"
Login: I am on the "Search" page
Logout: I am on the "/"
Logout: I wait for "1" seconds
Logout: I click on "Logout"
Logout: I am on the "Login" page

steps.name: Login: I am on the "/"

elements.name: I login into CMS application and check for create, view and edit permission for the user

steps.name: User Roles: I visit CMS application "/"
User Roles: I wait for "1" seconds
User Roles: I fill "k900374" in "New Username"
User Roles: I click on "Next"
User Roles: I wait for "1" seconds
User Roles: I fill "pswpsw123" in "New Password"
User Roles: I click on "New login button"
User Roles: I am on the "Search" page
User Roles: I see "Add Item" button and I have "Yes" create permission
User Roles: I wait for "1" seconds
User Roles: I click on "Moderator dropdown"
User Roles: I wait for "1" seconds
User Roles: I select "Tactical checklist moderator" value in "Moderator"
User Roles: I wait for "1" seconds
User Roles: I see "Search" button I have "Yes" view permission to click and check for "TACTICAL_CHECKLIST-MODERATOR"
User Roles: I wait for "1" seconds
User Roles: I see "TACTICAL_CHECKLIST-MODERATOR"
User Roles: I wait for "1" seconds
User Roles: I see "Edit" icon I have "Yes" edit permission to click and check for "TACTICAL_CHECKLIST-MODERATOR"
User Roles: I wait for "1" seconds
User Roles: I click on "Moderator dropdown"
User Roles: I wait for "1" seconds
User Roles: I select "Operational checklist moderator" value in "Moderator"
User Roles: I wait for "1" seconds
User Roles: I see "Search" button I have "Yes" view permission to click and check for "OPERATIONAL_CHECKLIST-MODERATOR"
User Roles: I wait for "1" seconds
User Roles: I see "OPERATIONAL_CHECKLIST-MODERATOR"
User Roles: I wait for "1" seconds
User Roles: I see "Edit" icon have "No" edit permission and I check for "OPERATIONAL_CHECKLIST-MODERATOR"
User Roles: I wait for "2" seconds
User Roles: I click on "Logout"
